divs: Sighting Details(Reporting this for a friend who wishes to remain completely anonymous). He was walking outside on the north side of a building on Lake Street and Chicago Ave in South Minneapolis, MN. Looked up to the sky and saw what he thought to be a UFO. It was a white light barely bigger than the stars around it. It made a small U-shaped path through the sky and then disappeared out of the atmosphere. He laughed at the event.
